    "context": "_s + \" no longer suffers from a \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "c4025549c1dbe5900f231298cb112053787076910ba4a2cf5e669668bf25411c",
    "original": " suffers from a ",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "_s + \" suffers from a \" + this.m.Name"
  },
  {
    "key": "0757ca737f7cf2151fc960ba8836207a3c9c6c0d5d5004862b6c3f294a6fb617",
    "original": "A terrible drought is ailing %settlement% from what I hear. It's always been hard for the folks over there, but this time it's dire.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "d79802eca8a28e7d10d53dadffbc4d58d512e5f39ab0092a5b8bb2c54a803d4a",
    "original": "An unexpected heatwave burnt many of the local crops. There is less food available and prices are higher.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Description = \"An unexpected heatwave burnt many of the local crops. There is less food available and prices are higher.\""
  },
  {
    "key": "5d1c2ffad14c8678b57d5ed3a9d623d351756b62f96bdafb4a114f84c4081048",
    "original": "Drought",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.Name = \"Drought\""
  },
  {
    "key": "8f2e42906944186309b41f81c167b7536b9feb834c77d209cd2c55cd46f023a6",
    "original": "If you are as reckless as you look, you might make a quick crown selling food in %settlement%. A harsh drought has the people starving, so they'll pay anything to get something between their teeth.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  },
  {
    "key": "18e90912a9b9dcd5b853150fbaa05f27d01fe2adc58e233e36a91c0d0bea2219",
    "original": "Oh, son, I used to be a rainmaker over in %settlement%, but the fools chased me off! Now, admittedly, the village was suffering from a draught, but isn't that all the more reason to rely on me? Fools, I say!",
    "translation": "",
    "context": ""
  }
]